Their menu is Caribbean-themed and Peter and Alida continue to get new ideas for menu items as they visit the Caribbean in the winters. Diners rave about the views they can take in while sitting outside under the sun and enjoying a meal.  Blue Parrot Grill always offers fun, music, entertainment, full food menu including apps, burgers, sandwiches, salads, pasta, ribs, steaks, fish and more! Customers continue to come back for the excellent service along with the delicious food. Some favorite menu items include the Ahi Ahi tuna, the Gator bites and the grilled plantains. The options range from seafood to burgers, chips to coleslaw and anything in between! Blue Parrot prides itself on the fresh, daily preparation of its seafood!
